{"tid":1565303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"律政司：被告冼嘉豪被控抗拒警員X及警長Y執行職責","createTime":"2019-09-13T05:52:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T18:06:22.000Z","uid":42188,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9e3a758ba1922709df28090b0779d2db0e26fdb7","tid":1565303,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:52:25.000Z","msg":"6.12大批示威者包圍立法會，阻止《逃犯條例》修訂草案恢復二讀，及後演變成激烈警民衝突。事隔三個月，警方落案起訴一名21歲救生員，控以一項暴動及兩項抗拒警務人員罪，案件今早提堂。記者發現，控罪書內容有違一般做法，抗拒警務人員控罪詳情只列出警員編號，未有列明警員姓名。隸屬有組織罪案及三合會調查科的案件主管、高級督察孔繁康在記者追問下，只著傳媒向警察公共關係科查詢，又辯稱「慣例唔係永遠㗎嘛」，反問記者為何提出質疑。<br />\n<br />\n被告冼嘉豪（21歲）被控於今年6月12日在中環立法會道立法會綜合大樓公眾入口外，連同其他身份不詳人士參與暴動，以及抗拒執行職責的警務人員，即警長34730和警員20338。"},{"pid":"3e4e36ecf769437957eec740ad7dc5dca52950df","tid":1565303,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:52:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"070d30792053dc2d67e94a6723779c26a763dc52","tid":1565303,"uid":76776,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:53:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1755036e3225f905b038935e8df7f1e09402f82d","tid":1565303,"uid":25108,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"070d30792053dc2d67e94a6723779c26a763dc52","tid":1565303,"uid":76776,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"c